During the Covid-19 crisis, it is essential for companies to keep on communicating. During the Covid-19 crisis, Creamer Media is offering companies exposure to our readership, who are decision-makers in South African industry and mining. Creamer Media has invited companies and public relations firms to communicate free of charge on Engineering News Online or MiningWeekly.com, by submitting press releases, company profiles, product profiles, or by requesting that Creamer Media write up such material. To make use of this marketing opportunity, or to find out more, please email reinette@engineeringnews.co.za.